  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 22.2,
    "text": "It's been hard to live without you, hard as death to figure out you."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.0,
    "end": 42.04,
    "text": "I've spent too long navigating bingo balls, gate B, Tennessee, 3C."
  },
  {
    "start": 42.68,
    "end": 49.42,
    "text": "And I don't like the things I see, these nameless faces around me, loneliness, I'm in deep."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.24,
    "end": 57.42,
    "text": "I want to find the ground, find a new position, feel my father's farm beneath my feet."
  },
  {
    "start": 58.92,
    "end": 59.98,
    "text": "My poor father's farm beneath my feet."
  },
  {
    "start": 59.98,
    "end": 60.0,
    "text": "My poor father's farm beneath my feet."
  },
  {
    "start": 60.0,
    "end": 65.84,
    "text": "My heart back in its full upright position, see what I can see."
  },
  {
    "start": 66.92,
    "end": 74.86,
    "text": "Oh, how it pleases me to see this, this town again, how my heart wants to believe I'm home."
  },
  {
